{"tid":2284441,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"記協申遊行被警拒　上訴委員會：倘政務司長准許會批准遊行","createTime":"2020-11-13T10:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T10:59:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"34dd4ae4236d7a434285030457d3aedda77d7fc2","tid":2284441,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"【17：50更新】港台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲被指進行車輛查冊時作出虛假陳述，案件上周提堂。蔡玉玲被捕及被控引起新聞界等廣泛爭議。香港記者協會計劃後日（15日）在港島區舉辦遊行，抗議警方濫捕，並要求查冊機制加設傳媒選項，但警方昨（12日）發出反對通知書。記協提出上訴，公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會聆訊今午（13日）3時舉行，上訴委員會傍晚近6時作出一致決定，指出若上訴人不遲於明天（14日），即計劃遊行的前一天取得政務司長的准許，委員會批准上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201113/s00001/1605251084043/%e8%a8%98%e5%8d%94%e7%94%b3%e9%81%8a%e8%a1%8c%e8%a2%ab%e6%8b%92-%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%e5%a7%94%e5%93%a1%e6%9c%83-%e5%80%98%e6%94%bf%e5%8b%99%e5%8f%b8%e9%95%b7%e5%87%86%e8%a8%b1%e6%9c%83%e6%89%b9?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201113%2Fs00001%2F1605251084043%2F%25e8%25a8%2598%25e5%258d%2594%25e7%2594%25b3%25e9%2581%258a%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258b%2592-%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583-%25e5%2580%2598%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%258f%25b8%25e9%2595%25b7%25e5%2587%2586%25e8%25a8%25b1%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%2589%25b9%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=e5e4e88d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201113%2Fs00001%2F1605251084043%2F%25e8%25a8%2598%25e5%258d%2594%25e7%2594%25b3%25e9%2581%258a%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258b%2592-%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4%25e5%25a7%2594%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%259c%2583-%25e5%2580%2598%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%258f%25b8%25e9%2595%25b7%25e5%2587%2586%25e8%25a8%25b1%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%2589%25b9%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=444a24c8\" data-auto-link ta